    addNode(104, "highschool.txt", "txt", "4.0 K", "2026-03-21", "High School Education (2022–2026)\nMircea cel Bătrân National College, Rm. Vâlcea, Romania\n\nKey Skills & Knowledge Acquired:\n\n- C++ Programming:\n    • Algorithmic thinking and problem-solving\n    • Data structures: vectors, matrices\n    • Basics of graphs, dynamic programming, and greedy algorithms\n\n- Machine Learning Foundations:\n    • Data manipulation and analysis in Python\n    • Applied basic ML algorithms:\n        - Linear Regression\n        - Logistic Regression\n        - k-Nearest Neighbors (k-NN)\n        - Random Forest", 4);
